# HEYDAY project context

**GOAL** — You are working on HEYDAY, a real estate operations platform (Express/SQLite API + React/Vite SPA). Path: `/Users/rexramza/Desktop/heyday`. User requirements are acceptance criteria, not nice-to-haves. Match mockups/screenshots exactly when provided.

## STACK

- Monorepo root: `package.json` runs `npm run dev` (nodemon API :3001 + Vite client :5173)
- Server: Node ESM, Express, better-sqlite3 (`heyday.db` or `DATABASE_PATH`), JWT auth via cookie, `foreign_keys ON`
- Client: React 18, React Router, Tailwind, Vite proxy `/api` → localhost:3001
- Build: `npm run build` (client only). No commits unless user asks.

## DEPLOY (Railway — live)

- Repo: `github.com/R3xRamza/heyday`
- URL: `https://heyday-production-ce72.up.railway.app`
- `railway.toml`: build client + `npm start` (production serves SPA from `client/dist`)
- Env: `NODE_ENV=production`, `JWT_SECRET`, `CLIENT_URL` (full `https://` URL), `DATABASE_PATH=/data/heyday.db` with Volume at `/data`
- Local `heyday.db` is gitignored; Railway starts fresh unless volume seeded or data imported

## DEV

- `npm run dev` from heyday root
- Default login seeded: `admin@heyday.com` / `admin123`
- Scripts: `clear-transactions`, `import-crm`, `seed-sample-transactions`

## REPO LAYOUT

- `server/index.js` — app entry, mounts `/api/*` routes with `authMiddleware`
- `server/routes/` — auth, crm, tasks, transactions, marketing, checklists, team, revenue, gmail
- `server/lib/` — migrate.js, business logic (transactionParties, applyChecklists, marketingCalendar, activity, etc.)
- `server/db.js` — SQLite init + `runMigrations()`; `DATABASE_PATH` env overrides default `heyday.db` path
- `client/src/App.jsx` — all routes
- `client/src/pages/` — screen-level components
- `client/src/components/` — shared UI (Sidebar, DashboardLayout, TopNav, marketing/*, etc.)
- `client/src/context/SidebarContext.jsx` — collapsible sidebar state (`sidebar-collapsed-v1`)
- `client/src/utils/format.js` — formatDate, formatCurrency, shortAddress, DateText pattern
- `client/src/index.css` — global + `.calendar-grid` (7 cols), `.marketing-calendar-*` styles

## ROUTES (client)

- `/login`, `/crm`, `/crm/:id` (contacts)
- `/tasks`, `/tasks/:userId` (team + per-user task dashboards, calendar view)
- `/transactions`, `/transactions/:id` (list + TransactionManager workspace)
- `/marketing` (Marketing Calendar)
- `/checklists` (template editor)
- `/revenue`, `/team-ops`

## API (server; all except `/api/auth` need session cookie)

- `/api/crm` — contacts (FUB import fields: birthday, anniversary, etc.)
- `/api/tasks` — team tasks; query: `assigned_to`, `transaction_id`, `due_after`, `due_before`, `transaction_only`
- `/api/transactions` — CRUD, parties, activity, checklists, DELETE (delete activity before tasks — FK)
- `/api/marketing` — calendar posts, platform-goals, birthdays range
- `/api/checklists` — template + template_tasks CRUD

## AUTH

- Client fetch: always `credentials: 'include'`
- `ProtectedRoute` wraps authenticated pages
- `DashboardLayout` = Sidebar + TopNav + main; sidebar 260px expanded / 72px collapsed; main margin follows `sidebarWidth`
- `SidebarContext` in `App.jsx`; collapse persisted in `sidebar-collapsed-v1`

## DESIGN SYSTEM

- Brand: feather (#134041), feather-alt, sky, lemon, off-white bg
- Tailwind tokens: primary-container, secondary, surface-*, on-surface-variant
- `html` font-size 18px (`index.css`)
- Logo: import from `client/src/assets/heyday-logo.png` (NOT `/public` path alone)
- Sidebar width 260px expanded, 72px collapsed; main `marginLeft` from `SidebarContext` (not hardcoded)
